      },
      "date": "2014-11-07 08:44:24.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nHi Jinshan,\n\nWhile applying http://review.whamcloud.com/10003 to Lustre b2_5 branch, there were a lot of conflicts because the changes from cfs_atomic_* to atomic_*, cfs_list_* to list_*, and seq_file, etc. were not landed on Lustre b2_5 branch.\n\nSo, I have to manually apply the patch to bypass those changes. Could you please review the patch in detail in comparison with the original patch in http://review.whamcloud.com/10003 ? Thank you!",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
    {
