      },
      "date": "2014-11-07 21:29:35.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> https://build.hpdd.intel.com/job/lustre-reviews/28228/ : FAILURE\n\nerror: 'const struct cl_page' has no member named 'cp_vmpage'\n\nI just found that \"cp_vmpage\" was introduced by patch http://review.whamcloud.com/7895 on master branch. However, we're not going to back-port this patch to b2_5 branch. So, we have to resolve the conflicts in cl_page_vmpage() and lru_page_busy() here.\n\nJinshan, could you please give me some suggestions?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
