        "subject": "LU-5812 osc: remove obd_unstable_pages from osc_announce_cached",
        "message": "LU-5812 osc: remove obd_unstable_pages from osc_announce_cached\n\nThe following patch on master branch removed the obd_unstable_pages\ntracking:\nLustre-commit: 48eceeec98da3db2c93d980bb5f7e1c1f7c333cc\nLustre-change: http://review.whamcloud.com/10003\n\nHowever, the codes depend on the patches for LU-3321 that are not in\nLustre b2_5 branch. So, this patch only removes the obd_unstable_pages\ntracking from osc_announce_cached() so as to quiet the error message.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jian Yu <jian.yu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I07d558a3fb62a679f3e50779b605719fcdf3e0ee\n"
      },
